Design tokens (vibe lock)
- Tile vibe: Pastel (soft Beach-Day accents)
- Corners: Pill (16px)
- Shadow: Soft (subtle drop; low elevation)

Surface tokens
- bg/app: light neutral
- bg/tile: white
- border/frame: light cool gray
- shadow/soft: low-opacity blur
- ink/main: near-black
- ink/dim: medium gray

Accent tokens (examples)
- kpi/cogs: soft amber
- kpi/labor: soft sky
- kpi/prime: soft teal
- kpi/bank: soft cyan
- kpi/profit: soft butter yellow
- marquee/bg: soft lavender

Why: matches our color boards (grayscale + Beach Day + pastels) and keeps the scenic TopBar readable.
Hex tokens
- ink/main: #2A2C34
- ink/dim:  #787D85
- frame:    #E1E2E6
- bg/app:   #F0F1F5
- bg/tile:  #FFFFFF
- shadow/soft: rgba(0,0,0,0.18)

KPI accents (pastel)
- kpi/cogs:   #F8D5AA
- kpi/labor:  #C1DCEE
- kpi/prime:  #C6E2D6
- kpi/bank:   #BDDBE6
- kpi/profit: #F9F1C7
- marquee/bg: #CCBAF6
Score → color thresholds (global)
- 0–39  = red (poor)
- 40–69 = amber (watch)
- 70–100 = green (good)

Per-metric direction
- Sales: higher = better
- Net Profit: higher = better
- COGS %: lower = better
- Labor %: lower = better
- Prime %: lower = better
- Bank balance: higher = better
- Online views: higher = better
- Review score: higher = better